    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gr: 1. Un tretcha Gadda Ose-\nnus Ela Dehla / ta Isra-\netu Rehnina/tappe Isfi\njus Akafa ta Rehnixa no Juhta\nDehls par Rehnizu pahe Juhtu.\n2. Un wiꞥſch bija diwidefmits\nun peezus Gaddus wezz/ kad\nwiꞥſch par Rehnixu tappe / un\nwaldija diwidefmits un dewinwe\nGaddus Jerusaleme/ un winna\nMahtei bija Abi Wahrdn/ Sa-\nkarijafa Metta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas darrija/ kas ta\nKUNGAM labbi patifke/ itt\npatt/ ka winna Tehws Dahwi\nbij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
