      "text": "Wiꞥſch ustizzeja tam KUN-\nGAM Israeta Deewam / 1\npehz winzu ne bija tahds\nwiꞥſch starp wiﬀeem kehutnee\nno Jubda/ ir preektch winna\nbija tahds bijts.\n"
